org.jpokemon.pmapi.util
Class ExperienceCurve

java.lang.Object
  org.jpokemon.pmapi.util.ExperienceCurve

public final class ExperienceCurve
extends Object

Defines the available experience curves for a Pokémon. For justification, see the entry in Bulbapedia. This class also contains static methods to retrieve the appropriate curve by name or byte identifier.
